#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:478
msgid ""
"To configure a FreeBSD system as an IPv6 client with a static IPv6 address "
"it is necessary to set the IPv6 address."
msgstr ""
"FreeBSD 시스템을 고정 IPv6 주소를 가진 IPv6 클라이언트로 구성하려면 IPv6 주소"
"를 설정해야 합니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:480
msgid "Execute the following commands to meet the requirements:"
msgstr "요구 사항을 충족하려면 다음 명령을 실행합니다:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:484
