#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:574
msgid "Authenticate the station"
msgstr "스테이션 인증"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:575
msgid "Configure an IP address or use DHCP."
msgstr "IP 주소를 구성하거나 DHCP를 사용."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:577
msgid "The following sections discuss each step."
msgstr "다음 섹션에서는 각 단계에 대해 설명합니다."

#. type: Title ===
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:579
#, no-wrap
msgid "Quick Start to Connect to a Wireless Network"
msgstr "무선 네트워크에 연결하기 위한 빠른 시작"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:582
msgid ""
"Connecting FreeBSD to an existing wireless network is a very common "
"situation."
msgstr "FreeBSD를 기존 무선 네트워크에 연결하는 것은 매우 일반적인 상황입니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:584
msgid "This procedure shows the steps required:"
msgstr "이 절차는 필요한 단계를 보여줍니다:"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:586
msgid ""
"The first step will be to obtain the SSID (Service Set Identifier) and PSK "
"(Pre-Shared Key) for the wireless network from the network administrator."
msgstr ""
"첫 번째 단계는 네트워크 관리자로부터 무선 네트워크의 SSID(Service Set "
"Identifier, 서비스 세트 식별자)와 PSK(Pre-Shared Key, 사전 공유 키)를 받는 것"
"입니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:588
msgid ""
"The second step will be to add an entry for this network to [.filename]#/etc/"
"wpa_supplicant.conf#. If the file does not exist, create it:"
msgstr ""
"두 번째 단계는 이 네트워크에 대한 항목을 [.filename]#/etc/wpa_supplicant."
"conf# 에 추가하는 것입니다. 파일이 없는 경우 파일을 생성합니다:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:595
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"network={\n"
" ssid=\"myssid\" <.>\n"
" psk=\"mypsk\" <.>\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
"network={\n"
" ssid=\"myssid\" <.>\n"
" psk=\"mypsk\" <.>\n"
"}\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:598
msgid ""
"Is the SSID of the wireless network. Replace it with the name of the "
"wireless network."
msgstr "무선 네트워크의 SSID입니다. 무선 네트워크의 이름으로 바꿉니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:599
msgid ""
"Is the PSK of the wireless network. Replace it with the password of the "
"wireless network."
msgstr "무선 네트워크의 PSK입니다. 무선 네트워크의 비밀번호로 바꿉니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:601
msgid ""
"The third step will be to add the network entry to configure the network on "
"startup:"
msgstr ""
"세 번째 단계는 시작 시 네트워크를 구성하기 위해 네트워크 항목을 추가하는 것입"
"니다:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:606
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# sysrc wlans_iwn0=\"wlan0\"\n"
"# sysrc ifconfig_wlan0=\"WPA DHCP\"\n"
msgstr ""
"# sysrc wlans_iwn0=\"wlan0\"\n"
"# sysrc ifconfig_wlan0=\"WPA DHCP\"\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:609
msgid ""
"And the last step will be the restart `netif` service executing the "
"following command:"
msgstr ""
"마지막 단계는 다음 명령을 실행하여 `netif` 서비스를 재시작하는 것입니다:"

#. type: Title ===
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:616
#, no-wrap
msgid "Basic Wireless Configuration"
msgstr "기본 무선 구성"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:621
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The first step will be to configure the wireless network card to an "
#| "interface.  To find out what wireless network cards are in the system "
