#. type: Title ===
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:684
#, no-wrap
msgid "Connection and Authentication to a Wireless Network"
msgstr "무선 네트워크에 연결 및 인증"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:689
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Once a wireless network has been selected from the list of scanned "
#| "networks, it is necessary to perform the connection ant the "
