msgstr "WPA2/WPA/Personal로 인증"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:694
msgid ""
"The authentication process in a wireless network is managed by man:"
"wpa_supplicant[8]."
msgstr ""
"무선 네트워크의 인증 프로세스는 man:wpa_supplicant[8] 에 의해 관리됩니다."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:697
msgid ""
"The man:wpa_supplicant[8] configuration will be made in the [.filename]#/etc/"
"wpa_supplicant.conf# file.  For more information, see man:wpa_supplicant."
"conf[5]."
msgstr ""
"man:wpa_supplicant[8] 구성은 [.filename]#/etc/wpa_supplicant.conf# 파일에서 "
"이루어집니다.  자세한 내용은 man:wpa_supplicant.conf[5] 를 참조하세요."

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:699
msgid ""
"Once the scanning of the wireless networks has been carried out, a network "
"has been chosen and have the password (PSK), that information will be added "
"to the file [.filename]#/etc/wpa_supplicant.conf# as in the following "
"example:"
msgstr ""
"무선 네트워크 검색이 수행되고 네트워크가 선택되고 비밀번호(PSK)가 있으면 다"
"음 예시와 같이 해당 정보가 [.filename]#/etc/wpa_supplicant.conf# 파일에 추가"
"됩니다:"

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:707
