"network={\n"
"        scan_ssid=1 <.>\n"
"        ssid=\"FreeBSD\" <.>\n"
"        psk=\"12345678\" <.>\n"
"}\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/network/_index.adoc:710
msgid ""
"SSID scan technique. Only need to use this option if the network is hidden."
